{{#>FullHtmlLayout}}
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
    style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
    <tr
        style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
        <td class="content-block"
            style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; margin: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0 0 10px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;"
            valign="top">
            {{OrganizationName}} seat count has been automatically increased to {{CurrentSeatCount}}.
            Your organization is currently configured to purchase seats {{#if LimitedAutoscaling}}up to a maximum of
            {{MaxSeatCount}}{{/if}} to accommodate all invites.
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr
        style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
        <td class="content-block"
            style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; margin: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0 0 10px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;"
            valign="top">
            To update your autoscale settings:
            <ol>
                <li>Log in to your <a
                        href="https://vault.bitwarden.com/#/organizations/{{{OrganizationId}}}/settings/subscription">Web
                        Vault</a> and open your Organization.</li>
                <li>Open the <b>Settings</b> tab and select <b>Subscription</b> from the left-hand menu.</li>
                <li>Click the <b>Autoscale Seats</b> button.</li>
                <li>Update your preferences.</li>
                <li>Click <b>Submit</b>.</li>
            </ol>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr
        style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
        <td class="content-block last"
            style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 25px; margin: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;"
            valign="top">
            For more information, please refer to the following help article: <a
                href="https://bitwarden.com/help/article/managing-users/#autoscale">https://bitwarden.com/help/article/managing-users/#autoscale</a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
{{/FullHtmlLayout}}
